p-content/uploads/2024/09/English-Teacher@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/English-Teacher@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/English-Teacher@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/english-teacher">English Teacher</a>向<em>NME</em>讲述了他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-win-the-2024-mercury-prize-for-this-could-be-texas-3791098">在 2024 年水星奖的历史性胜利，</a>并分享了如何努力利用他们的平台帮助英国艺术家争取一个更公平的世界。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-english-teacher-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-3495785">封面上的英语老师：来自英国吉他音乐中心的重要声音</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支利兹乐队和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-english-teacher-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-3495785"><em>NME</em>封面明星</a>——由主唱 Lily Fontaine、吉他手 Lewis Whiting、鼓手 Douglas Frost 和贝斯手 Nicholas Eden 组成——昨晚（9 月 5 日）凭借备受赞誉的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/english-teacher-this-could-be-texas-debut-album-review-tracklist-radar-3600231">《This Could</a> 》夺得胜利<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-to-english-teacher-winning-the-2024-mercury-prize-3791096">，引起了粉丝们的议论</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/english-teacher-this-could-be-texas-debut-album-review-tracklist-radar-3600231">Be Texas&#39;</a> – 击败了来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghetts">Ghetts</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corinne-bailey-rae">Corinne Bailey Rae</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beth-gibbons">Beth Gibbons</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-cant-swim">Barry Can&#39;t Swim</a>等的激烈竞争。</p><p>这是自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/young-fathers-2-13-1232165">2014 年爱丁堡年轻父亲乐队 (Young Fathers) 获奖</a>以来，首个非伦敦艺人获得水星奖。</p><p>在 Abbey Roads Studio 颁奖典礼上，乐队接受<em>NME</em>采访时表示，他们没想到这张专辑会得到如此高的评价，并回顾了这场胜利对他们意味着什么。</p><p> “这张专辑的反响令人难以置信，我们根本没想到会这样。我们实际上非常担心并期待相反的情况，所以这是超现实的，”弗罗斯特解释道。 “我觉得我需要很长一段时间才能理解这一点。消息一公布，我的整个身体就停止运转了。”</p><p>歌手莉莉·方丹 (Lily Fontaine) 表示同意，称这一天是“我一生中最美好的一天，包括我的婚礼和葬礼”，而怀廷则补充道，展望未来，“需要付出很多努力才能超越这一天”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_keLW3ymDx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 54